divs: Sighting Details In my back yard in S. Miami,i saw, above a passenger jet at night 5 large white lights flash on and off the total width of the 5 lights was the same as the plane. I thought what was that? 2. sometime in 1991 driving south on I95 in Miami, i looked over to the west and saw 2 gigantic circles of lights, one moving vertcially, and the other horizontally around the other, a student of mine days later told me she saw the same thing. I thought OMG i'm seeing a ufo but couldn't stop to investigate.
Summary: Lights above a jet plane, giant circles of lights both in Miami, Florida
